column5: Got out for a couple hours yesterday afternoon.  Had a blast, caught lots of fish, no monsters, but a lot, and kept 50 between 6 of us for a fish fry.   The keepers    The video of the nonstop action, and my g/f's cold hands
nice video and some nice keepers wtg
haha good one!  I liked the video.  "pretend you didn't  see that one".
Great stuff, and the video was a very nice touch!  I'm still a big zero for 2 outings in the fish department thru the ice....LOL.
nice catch and vid.  and no hut...thats hardcore- for the cameraperson!
